<li>6/11/92 <a href="/heritage/library/categories/regulation/bg900.html">Regulatory Relief or Power Grab: Should Congress Expand FDA's Enforcement Authority?</a> by Paul H. Rubin.  (Backgrounder #900)
<li>4/10/92 <a href="/heritage/library/categories/regulation/bgup177.html">Deregulating the Housing Market: What Can Congress Do</a> by Carl F. Horowitz, Ph.D. (Backgrounder Update No. 177)



<li>4/10/92 <a href="/heritage/library/categories/regulation/em327.html">The Department of Justice: April Foolishness on Antitrust</a> by Edward L. Hudgins and Nancy Bord. (Executive Memorandum #327)
<li>4/3/92 <a href="http://www.townhall.com/heritage/library/categories/theory/ib173.html">The Private Property Rights Act: Forcing Federal Regulators To Obey the Bill of Rights</a> by William G. Laffer III. (Issues Bulletin No. 173)


