<P>
<LI>   Bryan T. Johnson, "Foreign Aid Wins Few Friends at the United Nations," Heritage Foundation <A HREF="/heritage/library/categories/forpol/fyi101.html"><I>F.Y.I.</I> No. 101</A>, May 13, 1996.

<P>
</OL>
<P>

