http://www.conservative.org:80/heritage/p_review/jan96/meese.html 204.71.237.88 19970208193043 text/html 27725
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 19:31:24 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 11-Jan-96 22:41:16 GMT
Content-length: 27537
